          how: "Hash node IDs onto ring (0 to 2^32). Hash key onto ring. Walk clockwise to find owner node. Virtual nodes: each physical node gets multiple positions on ring (e.g., 150 virtual nodes) — ensures even distribution even with heterogeneous nodes.",
